<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Email Alert</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        color: #111827;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
     .header {
        background-color: #0f172a;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>{{health}}</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Email Verification Pending</h2>
        <p>Hello {{to}},</p>
        <p>
          This is a reminder that you need to verify your email within <strong>7 days</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          If verification is not completed within this period, your email and associated data will be <strong>deleted</strong> from our system.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
          If you did not initiate this process, you can safely ignore this message.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} {{health}}. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
